database.name: MetabolomicsWorkbench
database.description: The Metabolomics Workbench will serve as a national and international repository for metabolomics data and metadata and will provide analysis tools and access to metabolite standards, protocols, tutorials, training, and more.

entry.name: Timecourse on RAW 264.7 cells treated with Kdo2-Lipid A and compactin
entry.description: Lipidomics studies on macrophages - RAW 264.7 cells treated with Kdo2-Lipid A and compactin. Experiments were conducted with RAW264.7 cells fed 10% fetal calf serum. 8-timepoint study: Measurements were taken at 0, 0.5,1,2,4,8, 12, and 24hrs for: (i) compactin, (ii) Kdo2-Lipid A, (iii) compactin + Kdo2-Lipid A. and (iv) control
